node.title: Fire crews battle large blaze in Motueka industrial building
node.description: The fire is close to the town's main street.
node.content: ["Fire and Emergency New Zealand (FENZ) is attending a large fire in an old industrial building in central Motueka.\n", "A FENZ spokesperson says the blaze is in an area without hydrants, so five tankers are among the 16 fire engines at the scene.", "FENZ says the blaze is not far from the main road in Motueka and there are other old factory buildings nearby.", "The fire is not yet under control.", "RNZ"]
